text: Ani tyancyasobata itara dona taruna karagrhata ale. Tyancyapaiki ekajana mhanala, mi svapnata svatahla daru galatana pahile ahe, ani dusara mhanala, mi svapnata kaya pahato ki mi apalya dokyavara bhakari thevalya aheta, jyanna paksi khata aheta. Tumhi yaca artha (khulasa) amhala sangava. Amhala tara tumhi gunavana disata
